The Public Affairs Section of the Extraordinary Chambers in the Courts of Cambodia (ECCC) has the honour of inviting representatives of media to a press briefing in advance of Trial Chamber’s hearing in Case 002/02 against Khieu Samphan and Nuon Chea which will resume on 27 July 2015.
The Trial Chamber will shift its focus to Trapeang Thma Dam in the Northwest Zone, the third and final worksite in Case 002/02.
The press briefing will take place on Thursday 23 July 2015 from 10:00 – 11:00 am at Bophana Audiovisual Resource Center, located at 64, 200 Oknha Men, Phnom Penh.
This Press Briefing will be conducted in Khmer.
